title: Munditia daedala
text:
Munditia daedala is a <a href="species">species</a> of small <a href="sea%20snail">sea snail</a>, a <a href="marine%20%28ocean%29">marine</a> <a href="gastropod">gastropod</a> <a href="mollusk">mollusk</a>, in the <a href="Family%20%28biology%29">family</a> <a href="Liotiidae">Liotiidae</a>.
Distribution.
This marine species occurs off <a href="Japan">Japan</a>.
